  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: Fit For Emperors And Kings
---
Hu Tzu said, "Just now I appeared to him with the Pattern of Earth -
still and silent, nothing moving, nothing standing up. He probably saw
in me the Workings of Virtue Closed Off. Try bringing him around
again."
